1
00:00:06,131 --> 00:00:08,049
And the person behind you...

2
00:00:19,310 --> 00:00:21,271
Lu... Lucifer?

3
00:00:22,063 --> 00:00:23,106
Long time no see, Siren

4
00:00:23,606 --> 00:00:24,858
It's been a while

5
00:00:26,651 --> 00:00:27,277
Your highness!

6
00:00:27,861 --> 00:00:28,570
Sincere apologies, your highness!

7
00:00:28,737 --> 00:00:29,696
I just...

8
00:00:30,155 --> 00:00:32,282
You ran, so you gotta pay the price

9
00:00:35,535 --> 00:00:36,077
- Hey!

10
00:00:37,495 --> 00:00:38,997
This is not why we came here

11
00:00:39,748 --> 00:00:40,582
Let go!

12
00:00:41,082 --> 00:00:41,791
No

13
00:00:42,333 --> 00:00:44,878
We came to fix this blood bond thing

14
00:00:45,336 --> 00:00:46,588
Beating them up

15
00:00:46,921 --> 00:00:48,256
won't solve anything

16
00:00:58,933 --> 00:01:00,685
Let's ask about that first

17
00:01:01,144 --> 00:01:03,271
What do we do about this?

18
00:01:41,351 --> 00:01:42,936
So you two are currently

19
00:01:43,895 --> 00:01:46,272
bound by blood?

20
00:01:48,274 --> 00:01:51,027
To be exact, I drank his blood,

21
00:01:51,194 --> 00:01:53,154
and some strange bond formed

22
00:01:56,324 --> 00:01:58,535
An unstable bond...

23
00:02:01,412 --> 00:02:04,666
In that state, your energies are being shared

24
00:02:04,916 --> 00:02:06,543
So if you're apart for too long,

25
00:02:06,626 --> 00:02:09,337
your bodies start having adverse reactions

26
00:02:11,297 --> 00:02:13,925
Then is there a way to undo this?

27
00:02:14,759 --> 00:02:17,971
To be precise, you can't undo it

28
00:02:18,138 --> 00:02:20,014
You must complete it

29
00:02:21,182 --> 00:02:22,183
Complete it?

30
00:02:24,227 --> 00:02:25,603
In 15 days,

31
00:02:26,020 --> 00:02:27,772
on the night of the full moon,

32
00:02:28,314 --> 00:02:29,065
- Minu

33
00:02:29,274 --> 00:02:31,442
- must bite Prince Lucifer's neck

34
00:02:32,235 --> 00:02:33,486
I'm the one getting bitten?

35
00:02:35,488 --> 00:02:38,283
It's not getting bitten
It's restoring the balance

36
00:02:39,617 --> 00:02:42,245
Completing the blood bond

37
00:02:43,454 --> 00:02:46,583
Once that happens,
your bodies will be in balance,

38
00:02:46,749 --> 00:02:49,961
and you'll be fine even when apart

39
00:02:51,546 --> 00:02:55,258
- By then, Minu's condition
should be fully healed, too

40
00:02:56,593 --> 00:02:57,719
So...

41
00:02:58,803 --> 00:03:01,973
we have to stay together until then?

42
00:03:07,979 --> 00:03:11,399
There is one bypass, though...

43
00:03:15,069 --> 00:03:16,988
If you can purify Minu's blood

44
00:03:17,238 --> 00:03:19,157
and have Prince Lucifer drink it,

45
00:03:19,908 --> 00:03:21,576
you can be apart for some time

46
00:03:21,576 --> 00:03:24,412
without any adverse reactions

47
00:03:24,787 --> 00:03:26,789
It varies from person to person,

48
00:03:27,123 --> 00:03:30,418
but about six hours should be fine

49
00:03:31,336 --> 00:03:32,128
Purify?

50
00:03:33,046 --> 00:03:33,630
How?

51
00:03:34,214 --> 00:03:35,673
Well...

52
00:03:41,638 --> 00:03:42,263
Uh...

53
00:03:42,722 --> 00:03:44,182
In the human world,

54
00:03:44,432 --> 00:03:46,434
people donate blood, right?

55
00:03:47,018 --> 00:03:49,062
Just draw clean blood and drink it

56
00:03:50,313 --> 00:03:52,106
That'll do, your highness

57
00:03:55,526 --> 00:03:56,277
Also,

58
00:03:57,237 --> 00:03:59,364
until the next lunar eclipse,

59
00:03:59,364 --> 00:04:00,031
be careful!

60
00:04:00,698 --> 00:04:02,617
Make sure to be safe

61
00:04:03,952 --> 00:04:04,494
Um...

62
00:04:06,704 --> 00:04:07,997
I have...

63
00:04:08,373 --> 00:04:10,250
a bad premonition

64
00:04:11,542 --> 00:04:12,669
Worry about yourself

65
00:04:13,461 --> 00:04:15,171
Still as prickly as ever, your highness

66
00:04:19,259 --> 00:04:20,260
By the way,

67
00:04:21,177 --> 00:04:22,262
you two

68
00:04:22,428 --> 00:04:25,682
actually look good together

69
00:04:26,224 --> 00:04:26,683
Excuse me?

70
00:04:26,849 --> 00:04:27,433
What?!

71
00:04:28,184 --> 00:04:29,727
Your compatibility reading shows

72
00:04:30,103 --> 00:04:33,189
that you're a perfect match

73
00:04:34,607 --> 00:04:35,275
What?

74
00:04:36,317 --> 00:04:37,527
What do you even mean...?

75
00:04:38,278 --> 00:04:39,028
I'm leaving

76
00:04:41,614 --> 00:04:42,907
Have a nice day

77
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:47,620
Oh, right

78
00:04:48,246 --> 00:04:51,040
The next full moon is 15 days from now!

79
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:52,542
At midnight!

80
00:04:52,709 --> 00:04:55,086
You must not forget this, Prince Lucifer!

81
00:05:04,053 --> 00:05:05,054
Next customer!

82
00:05:14,147 --> 00:05:15,815
This is the purified blood?

83
00:05:16,607 --> 00:05:18,651
It smells milder than I expected

84
00:05:20,236 --> 00:05:21,237
That's my precious blood

85
00:05:21,904 --> 00:05:23,281
Don't leave a single drop

86
00:05:24,782 --> 00:05:25,742
Once you drink that,

87
00:05:25,742 --> 00:05:28,161
we should be fine apart for a few hours

88
00:05:28,911 --> 00:05:29,912
So I'll go to work

89
00:05:33,291 --> 00:05:33,916
Oh!

90
00:05:34,375 --> 00:05:35,543
It's not as bad as I thought

91
00:05:36,669 --> 00:05:38,254
Don't tell me how it tastes

92
00:05:39,964 --> 00:05:42,884
Is it okay if I go out alone for a bit?

93
00:05:43,509 --> 00:05:45,720
I don't think you need to worry that much

94
00:05:46,220 --> 00:05:47,680
Can I go out?

95
00:05:48,389 --> 00:05:49,390
No, wait

96
00:05:49,766 --> 00:05:50,266
No...

97
00:05:51,351 --> 00:05:52,894
These days, if people see someone weird,

98
00:05:52,894 --> 00:05:55,563
they post photos online
and call the cops right away

99
00:05:57,607 --> 00:05:59,609
Do I really look that weird?

100
00:06:01,694 --> 00:06:03,363
Fangs popping out randomly

101
00:06:03,613 --> 00:06:04,489
Red eyes

102
00:06:05,031 --> 00:06:06,282
Even I'd report you

103
00:06:07,450 --> 00:06:08,576
Is that a compliment?

104
00:06:10,370 --> 00:06:11,120
No

105
00:06:11,537 --> 00:06:13,122
A one-way ticket to the police station

106
00:06:14,957 --> 00:06:16,959
Just get used to things a bit more first

107
00:06:17,794 --> 00:06:18,878
And make sure to lock the door

108
00:06:20,213 --> 00:06:21,047
If you behave,

109
00:06:21,631 --> 00:06:23,424
I'll bring you something delicious tonight

110
00:06:23,883 --> 00:06:25,551
Oh! Meat?

111
00:06:27,887 --> 00:06:29,263
Depends on how you behave

112
00:06:31,265 --> 00:06:32,266
I'll be back

113
00:06:33,976 --> 00:06:34,727
Okay

114
00:06:44,112 --> 00:06:45,279
Adapt?

115
00:06:46,906 --> 00:06:49,283
Me, adapting to the human world

116
00:07:43,212 --> 00:07:44,213
What is this?

117
00:07:45,256 --> 00:07:47,216
Why do I miss him so much?
